冰你你揀邊樣呀<br />\n成日大腸桿菌超標就屎屎屎 DLLM"},{"pid":"226953b1bc4a3baf97323a5793f4ca1f026de952","tid":394031,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:43:43.000Z","msg":"啲冰由朝放到晚你話有幾乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2bdfadc988fb42284726a38149e57aec24a5722","tid":394031,"uid":14758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T18:44:53.000Z","msg":"唔搞得次次食完放啲屁都勁撚臭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f31b65bdf168309c7c1c4c73ff745d4412608e","tid":394031,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T18:58:25.000Z","msg":"呢鑊食曬屎"},{"pid":"dd09e154338adc87afc8291487b9b7115b6325a9","tid":394031,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T19:11:16.000Z","msg":"粉嶺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0e941bbb907ba22ce46fdf4b0ae30434997a90","tid":394031,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T06:06:19.000Z","msg":"一定要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">走冰</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a2d8d81f5204aa16cab6376ebdfbca3a01e62e","tid":394031,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T06:25:51.000Z","msg":"幫趁M記同kfc的都係食屎狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe91d7498fdd5bf42018f6892e134a0edce8305","tid":394031,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T06:27:12.000Z","msg":"由細到大都走冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d2c02059f274e6981e6244abb6322b19466caf","tid":394031,"uid":126044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T06:27:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫趁M記同kfc的都係食屎狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" clas