12310235","tid":394031,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T07:00:38.000Z","msg":"其實快餐店有製冰機已經好左<br />\n試下驗埋茶記嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8818cde5f86c47e6c9c63325a414a3074c5983","tid":394031,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前舊登有巴打做制冰 話用黎碎冰既工具好污糟 仲會用鞋踩d冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇完個post之後淨係夠膽幫襯酒店凍飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他地方只會飲罐裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a934cb3572c464044d34da0f4a4d058199639a","tid":394031,"uid":137627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T07:03:08.000Z","msg":"連食屎都要加錢，香港人真係命賤"},{"pid":"8d8cc992a1ec871d94fdd0fd63dccd2f6d4946f1","tid":394031,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T07:21:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170909/large/1504950699_d7cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170909%2Flarge%2F1504950699_d7cb.png&h=6e4366fb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解追擊住粉嶺啲分店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全部都係香港大西北地方 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a846af5b1ecd6ef5e1c16f6640fa738906d779f","tid":394031,"uid":136015,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T07:21:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170909/large/1504950699_d7cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170909%2Flarge%2F1504950699_d7cb.png&h=6e4366fb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br